T1  - The Dynamic Impact of Product-Harm Crises on Brand Preference and Advertising Effectiveness: An Empirical Analysis of the Automobile Industry
AU  - Liu, Yan
AU  - Shankar, Venkatesh
Y1  - 2015/03/26
